                <p class="sec-lead reveal" style="transition-delay:.06s">Get up and running with the Deepfake Nexus API in under five minutes. All you need is an API key and any HTTP client.</p>

                <!-- 3D inline scene -->
                <div class="inline-3d reveal" style="height:220px;margin-bottom:28px;transition-delay:.1s">
