                <p class="sec-lead reveal" style="transition-delay:.06s">Register webhook endpoints to receive real-time push notifications when analyses complete or when critical threats are detected.</p>

                <div class="inline-3d reveal" style="height:220px;margin-bottom:28px;transition-delay:.08s">
                    <canvas id="WH3D"></canvas>
                    <div class="inline-3d-over">
                        <div class="i3d-corner i3d-tl"></div><div class="i3d-corner i3d-tr"></div>
                        <div class="i3d-corner i3d-bl"></div><div class="i3d-corner i3d-br"></div>
