                        <div style="padding:22px"><div style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px">AI Image Generator Module</div><div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--c3);line-height:1.85">Added <code style="color:var(--g)">/v1/image/generate</code> endpoint. Latent diffusion at up to 2048×2048. Python and Node SDKs updated. Batch generation support (up to 4 images per request).</div></div>
