                        <div style="padding:22px;border-right:1px solid var(--s);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;color:var(--c3)">v3.0.2<br><span style="color:var(--c4)">Feb 2026</span></div>
                        <div style="padding:22px"><div style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px">Performance & Accuracy</div><div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--c3);line-height:1.85">Email analysis latency reduced 34%. False positive rate on media detection reduced to &lt;0.1%. New transformer model for scam classification with 98.2% accuracy.</div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:160px 1fr;transition:background .3s" class="reveal" style="transition-delay:.1s">
                        <div style="padding:22px;border-right:1px solid var(--s);font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:8.5px;color:var(--c3)">v3.0.0<br><span style="color:var(--c4)">Jan 2026</span></div>
                        <div style="padding:22px"><div style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px">Platform Redesign & New API</div><div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--c3);line-height:1.85">Full API versioning. Webhook system launch. Batch endpoint beta. PHP SDK release. All endpoints now under <code style="color:var(--g)">/v1/</code> prefix.</div></div>
